         ¶ You wanna be         
      where you can see ¶       

01:48.375 --> 01:50.609
         ¶ Our troubles         
    are all the same ¶          

01:50.677 --> 01:54.613
      ¶ You wanna be where      
  everybody knows your name ¶   

01:56.316 --> 01:58.550
         ¶ You wanna go         
      where people know ¶       

